## Frontend environment variables (ShopAbhi)
#
# This CRA app currently hardcodes the backend base URL in code.
# If you want to switch between local and deployed backend, you can add env vars
# and update the code to read them (e.g. REACT_APP_API_BASE).
#
# Example (not used unless you wire it into the code):
# REACT_APP_API_BASE=http://localhost:5000

